And Hector with a round shield at their head, As when a star does through the clouds appear, And presently again is covered ;
Sometimes i' th' front was, sometimes in the rear Giving command ;
his arms like lightning show.
As mowers standing one rank 'gainst another, A field of barley or of wheat to mow ;
